column5: Shot this video footage out on my back deck also a couple of pictures i took also. I have four humming birds that frequents my feeders everyday. Love these cute little buggas.             Short video clip of one of the hummingbirds at one of my feeders on my back deck.     Nauti.

I was in your great little town yesterday, for some work. Did not get the chance to drop a line in the water as it was raining out! I left Hamilton and it was fine, I got to Jarvis and it started, too late to turn around for a better day.  Easton
Thanx so much father of three.  Easton you should have dropped me a line and let me known you were in town.
Beautiful! The hummingbird is definitely the "Mr. Bean" of the bird world!
Wonderful pics Tracy.  How's the reunion going?  Joey
Great pictures, a steady hand you have there!  They like the feeders with the perches better though.  They save more energy that way.  Pam
My appolgies for no reply sooner ladies. Joey u know allready from when we last spoke and thanx again.  Pam that is the only feeder i have with out perches the rest all have perches.......  Nauti.
